headline.main: London Lists 9 U.S. Fliers Killed in Action; 3 Others Are Missing, One Taken Prisoner

lead_paragraph: LONDON, Nov. 18 -- The names of thirteen American fliers, nine of whom have been killed, three missing and one taken prisoner were announced by the Air Ministry today. Five of those killed were members of the Eagle Squadron and the other four were with the Royal Canadian Air Force.
